            <a class= "topZ" href="/story/{{story.id}}">{{story.title}}</a>
            {{/ifEquals}}
          {{/each}}
          </div>
          <div class='page'>
            <div>
              <h1>Deserted Island</h1>
              <p class='text'>&emsp;Have you ever felt the turbulance of an airplane? It's not the best feeling, 
                being tossed around in the air with no landing in sight. That feeling I will never forget, I thought
                it would be my last day here on Earth, but I could not have been more wrong. Now here I am, just myself,
                the ocean in front of me, and the sand in between my toes. You may think to yourself, that sounds amazing! Let me 
                assure you, this is no vaction, I am stranded on an island. No one survivied the crash with me, at least I don't believe
                so. But the real question is what will I do from here? </p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div id='page-shading'></div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
